1
00:01:03,620 --> 00:01:05,850
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:09,730
[Episode 17]

3
00:01:11,090 --> 00:01:14,690
[Ciyuan Palace]

4
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,120
Mother!

5
00:01:28,150 --> 00:01:28,840
Mother.

6
00:01:29,070 --> 00:01:29,890
Nianzhao.

7
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,600
How have you been these days?

8
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,310
I'm fine.

9
00:01:33,509 --> 00:01:34,870
But you should visit less often.

10
00:01:34,870 --> 00:01:37,470
Don't let Xie Jiuzhao
take his anger out on you.

11
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,710
What happened?

12
00:01:52,100 --> 00:01:54,430
[Si]

13
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:03,130
[Si]

14
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:09,720
Jiuzhao killed Simo.

15
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,240
He took Jiang Li with him.

16
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:14,160
They've disappeared without a trace.

17
00:02:19,579 --> 00:02:22,860
[Si]

18
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:26,590
This is your birthday gift.

19
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:28,660
See if you like it.

20
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:30,930
[Si]

21
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:33,710
Yes. Thank you, Aunt.

22
00:02:33,900 --> 00:02:37,060
[Si]

23
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:49,210
Mother, please don't grieve too much.

24
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,590
Nianzhao.

25
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:55,280
Go quickly. Get as far away as possible.

26
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,120
Don't let him find you.

27
00:02:57,910 --> 00:02:58,680
Go!

28
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,000
Hurry up!

29
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,000
Go now!

30
00:03:06,910 --> 00:03:09,470
My Simo.

31
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,190
Zhao,

32
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:44,290
we should hurry back to the palace

33
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,280
before something unexpected happens.

34
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,590
It's alright, Li.

35
00:03:47,590 --> 00:03:49,030
We're not in a rush.

36
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:52,870
Just consider it you showing me around.

37
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:56,430
Alright... then.

38
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:03,080
Careful, don't fall.

39
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,040
Flower cakes for sale!

40
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,870
Sir, can I have two pieces, please?

41
00:04:05,870 --> 00:04:06,840
These are freshly made.

42
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,590
Here you go.

43
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,430
Thank you.

44
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:10,470
Come back after you've enjoyed them!

45
00:04:10,470 --> 00:04:11,000
Lanterns!

46
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:11,530
Let's go.

47
00:04:11,930 --> 00:04:12,750
Take a look at the lanterns.

48
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:14,350
These are festive lanterns!

49
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:16,430
When I was little, my mother taught me
how to make festive lanterns.

50
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:17,829
During the Lantern Festival,

51
00:04:17,829 --> 00:04:19,070
she would hold my hand,

52
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:20,040
carry festive lantern,

53
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,600
and take me to see the parade.

54
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,920
Then let's buy one.

55
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,680
Never mind.

56
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,190
We need to get going.

57
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:35,430
Look at this.

58
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,159
Look at this mask.

59
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,870
This mask is so unique!

60
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,360
Since the lady likes it so much,

61
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:04,830
hurry up and get her one.

62
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:08,010
Where's the money?

63
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,830
Thank you, sir.

64
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:14,390
Madam, you are truly blessed.

65
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,600
Do you like it, my dear?

66
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,120
Don't call me that.

67
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,720
We're not married yet.

68
00:05:25,870 --> 00:05:28,070
When can we get married then?

69
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:36,040
I'm going to look at the wind chimes.

70
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,990
What beautiful wind chimes!

71
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,310
This one is nice too.

72
00:05:47,310 --> 00:05:47,950
Yes.

73
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:49,950
So you bought this one?

74
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:50,830
Yes.

75
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,530
I wonder if my husband will like it.

76
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:57,060
He'll definitely like it.

77
00:07:02,290 --> 00:07:03,810
Xie Jiuzhao.

78
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:06,150
I was too stupid before.

79
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:09,040
Stupid enough to have expectations of you.

80
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,600
Now,

81
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:14,230
since you've made your choice,

82
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,430
this throne

83
00:07:17,510 --> 00:07:20,240
should be mine.

84
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:23,590
Buddha bless Nianzhao.

85
00:07:23,610 --> 00:07:24,650
Buddha bless Nianzhao.

86
00:07:24,650 --> 00:07:25,980
Buddha bless Nianzhao.

87
00:07:25,990 --> 00:07:27,510
Please, Buddha, bless Nianzhao.

88
00:07:27,510 --> 00:07:28,560
Please, Buddha, bless Nianzhao.

89
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,240
Buddha bless him.

90
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:41,750
Nianzhao.

91
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:43,909
Nianzhao.

92
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:44,560
Mother.

93
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:45,980
Are you alright?

94
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:48,560
Don't worry, Mother.

95
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,680
Xie Jiuzhao is unworthy of his position

96
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:53,240
and his luck has run out.

97
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:56,000
I reasoned with General Ling

98
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:57,800
and he felt duty-bound

99
00:07:58,159 --> 00:08:00,360
to help me restore proper order.

100
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:03,070
The palace guards

101
00:08:03,270 --> 00:08:06,190
are now all under my command.

102
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:09,190
Good. Good!

103
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:12,410
My years of planning
for you weren't in vain.

104
00:08:12,490 --> 00:08:14,290
But you, my child,

105
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:16,190
when did you become so decisive

106
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:17,870
that you even kept me in the dark?

107
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:19,830
Desperate times
call for desperate measures.

108
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:21,430
It's not too late

109
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,780
for you to know now.

110
00:08:23,190 --> 00:08:24,600
Since everything is settled,

111
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,830
at tomorrow morning's court,

112
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:27,560
I will announce it to the world.

113
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,430
We must not repeat
my mistakes of the past.

114
00:08:29,430 --> 00:08:30,830
That won't be necessary.

115
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:33,600
I have already prepared
the imperial decree.

116
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:37,080
However, Xie Jiuzhao is deeply scheming

117
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:39,120
and has hidden the imperial seal.

118
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:40,840
What?

119
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,180
It's happening again?

120
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:47,480
Without the imperial seal,
it's hard to win people's support.

121
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,680
I've already sent people to arrest him.

122
00:08:49,910 --> 00:08:53,150
If Xie Jiuzhao refuses
to surrender the imperial seal,

123
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:57,480
then I'll kill him.

124
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,730
When the time comes,

125
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:02,360
Mother, please help me

126
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:04,910
make sure Xie Jiuzhao

127
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:08,360
is completely disgraced

128
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:11,590
and can never recover.

129
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,420
Greetings, Your Majesty.

130
00:09:26,790 --> 00:09:30,390
I congratulate Your Majesty
on ascending the throne.

131
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,630
Ling.

132
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,360
Still calling me Ling?

133
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:42,200
Your Majesty hasn't forgotten

134
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,870
our agreement, have you?

135
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:47,150
I helped Your Majesty claim the throne,

136
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:51,120
and you promised to make me your Empress.

137
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,870
This way,

138
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:58,360
the Ling family's army will become
Your Majesty's strong support,

139
00:09:58,630 --> 00:10:02,080
ensuring the stability of the kingdom.

140
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:04,000
Report!

141
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:14,390
Where is Xie Jiuzhao?

142
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:15,870
When I arrived,

143
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:18,320
Xie Jiuzhao was already gone.

144
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:20,790
I could only bring Jiang Li back first.

145
00:10:21,550 --> 00:10:22,320
Useless!

146
00:10:24,150 --> 00:10:26,870
Tell me where Xie Jiuzhao is!

147
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:28,870
I was about to ask you the same thing,

148
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,080
Prince Nianzhao.

149
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,120
Stop pretending.

150
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,840
Weren't you two together?

151
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,840
Together?

152
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,480
I thought he came to rescue me,

153
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,670
but what happened?

154
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,630
After I helped him kill Xun Simo,

155
00:10:39,630 --> 00:10:41,270
he abandoned me and ran away.

156
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,360
Right now,

157
00:10:43,550 --> 00:10:46,080
I want to know where he is
even more than you do.

158
00:10:49,750 --> 00:10:50,440
Go.

159
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:53,670
At all costs,

160
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:56,720
bring Xie Jiuzhao back to me.

161
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,360
Yes, Your Majesty.

162
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,150
Also,

163
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:01,270
take her away,

164
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:03,910
but don't let her die.

165
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,200
Take her away.
